Package de.htw.berlin.polysun4diac.forte.datatypes

Package for the definitions of IEC 61499 data types.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DateAndTime
    Class for representing time stamps in the IEC 61499 DATE_AND_TIME format as represented in 4diac-RTE (FORTE).
    ForteTypeIDs
    Class for holding the supported FORTE type IDs that represent the IEC 61499 data types.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ForteDataType
    Enum for the supported IEC 61499 data types that can be sent to/received from FORTE.
